Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper deals with communication and synthesis of strategies for distributed agents. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper discusses undecidability results. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses solving games in continuous time. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper models the flow of time explicitly. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with synthesising strategies for agents to reach specified goals.
